content.html: Life lesson I wish I learned earlier: Never stop flirting with your significant other 💖 Make time for dates, even if you live together 💖 It takes effort to keep your spark alive. It doesn’t always have to be a huge effort. Just a cute note or a phone call to say hi 🥰
content.value:
Life lesson I wish I learned earlier:

Never stop flirting with your significant other 💖

Make time for dates, even if you live together 💖

It takes effort to keep your spark alive. It doesn’t always have to be a huge effort. Just a cute note or a phone call to say hi 🥰
